      "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListClasses_ctl00_LabelName\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.classes.cCZQpV0NmYE9qZoL]{Soldier}</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListClasses_ctl00_LabelName\">As a standard action, you can make a single attack against an enemy. If the attack hits and does not kill your enemy, you can expend 1 Resolve Point to force the creature to succeed at a Fortitude save or die. Once you&rsquo;ve used this ability on a creature (regardless of whether or not you forced it to attempt a Fortitude save), that creature is immune to your kill shot for 24 hours.</span></p>",
